sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as NestJS API
    participant Q as BullMQ (Redis)
    participant W as Worker
    participant AI as OpenAI API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant WS as WebSocket

    U->>API: POST /audio/upload (file)
    API->>DB: Save audio record (status: pending)
    API->>Q: Enqueue processing job
    API-->>U: 202 Accepted (audioId)

    Q->>W: Pick up job
    W->>WS: Emit progress (transcribing)
    W->>AI: Whisper transcription
    AI-->>W: Transcription text
    W->>DB: Save transcription

    W->>WS: Emit progress (analyzing)
    W->>AI: GPT-4o decompose into tasks
    AI-->>W: Task array
    W->>AI: GPT-4o generate tickets
    AI-->>W: Structured tickets (JSON)

    W->>DB: Save generated tickets
    W->>DB: Update audio status (completed)
    W->>WS: Emit progress (completed)
    WS-->>U: Real-time notification
